<i>noun</i>: 호들갑 [호들갑], 요란 [요란], 야단법석 [야ː단법썩], 안달복달 [안달복딸], 수선 [수선], 소란 [소란], 소동 [소동], 설레발 [설레발], 생난리 [생날리], 부산 [부산], 법석 [법썩], 난리 [날ː리] <i>verb</i>: 법석하다 [법써카다], 법석이다 [법써기다], 법석법석하다 [법썩뻡써카다], 법석대다 [법썩때다], 법석거리다 [법썩꺼리다] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>호들갑 [호들갑]</dt><br>
<dd>fuss; uproar; making a big deal; overreaction</dd><br>
<dd>가볍고 조심성이 없으며 야단스러운 말이나 행동.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of acting or speaking in an imprudent, careless, and boisterous manner.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>요란 [요란]</dt><br>
<dd>1. fuss; bustle</dd><br>
<dd>어수선하고 시끄러움.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being disordered and loud.</dd><br>
<dd>2. fuss; bustle</dd><br>
<dd>야단스러울 만큼 정도가 지나침.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being excessive to the point of being fussy.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>야단법석 [야ː단법썩]</dt><br>
<dd>fuss; bustle</dd><br>
<dd>시끄럽고 어수선하게 행동함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of making a noise and behaving in a disorderly manner.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>안달복달 [안달복딸]</dt><br>
<dd>fret; fuss</dd><br>
<dd>몹시 마음을 졸이고 조급하게 굴면서 몰아치는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being very nervous, impatient, and pushy.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>수선 [수선]</dt><br>
<dd>fuss</dd><br>
<dd>사람의 정신을 어지럽게 만드는 시끄러운 말이나 혼란스러운 행동.</dd><br>
<dd>Noisy or chaotic behavior that confuses one's mind.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>소란 [소란]</dt><br>
<dd>disturbance; fuss; commotion</dd><br>
<dd>시끄럽고 정신없게 복잡함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being noisy and hectic.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>소동 [소동]</dt><br>
<dd>disturbance; fuss; commotion</dd><br>
<dd>시끄럽게 떠들고 어지럽게 행동하는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of making a loud noise and causing a commotion.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>설레발 [설레발]</dt><br>
<dd>fuss</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일을 하기 전에 몹시 서두르며 시끄럽게 구는 행동.</dd><br>
<dd>The manner or state of being extremely hasty and loud before doing something.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>생난리 [생날리]</dt><br>
<dd>fuss</dd><br>
<dd>별다른 이유 없이 매우 시끄럽게 들볶아 대는 것.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of making a noisy hassle for no justifiable reason.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>부산 [부산]</dt><br>
<dd>bustle; fuss</dd><br>
<dd>정신이 없을 만큼 어지럽거나 시끄러움.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of being so noisy and disordered that one feels upset.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>법석 [법썩]</dt><br>
<dd>noise; fuss; uproar</dd><br>
<dd>소란스럽게 떠드는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A very loud scene.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>난리 [날ː리]</dt><br>
<dd>1. war; fight</dd><br>
<dd>전쟁이나 나라 안에서 일어난 싸움.</dd><br>
<dd>A war, or a fight that occurs within a country.</dd><br>
<dd>2. chaos; disorder; mess</dd><br>
<dd>홍수, 지진, 가뭄 등으로 질서가 어지러운 상태.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of being chaotic without order due to flood, earthquake, drought, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>3. noise; fuss</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 놀라거나 흥분하여 소란스럽게 떠드는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) The act of making a noise about something out of surprise or excitement.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>법석하다 [법써카다]</dt><br>
<dd>make a noise; fuss</dd><br>
<dd>소란스럽게 떠들다.</dd><br>
<dd>To make a loud noise.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>법석이다 [법써기다]</dt><br>
<dd>make a noise; fuss</dd><br>
<dd>소란스럽게 떠들다.</dd><br>
<dd>To make a loud noise.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>법석법석하다 [법썩뻡써카다]</dt><br>
<dd>make a noise; fuss</dd><br>
<dd>소란스럽게 자꾸 떠들다.</dd><br>
<dd>To make a loud noise repeatedly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>법석대다 [법썩때다]</dt><br>
<dd>make a noise; fuss</dd><br>
<dd>소란스럽게 자꾸 떠들다.</dd><br>
<dd>To make a loud noise repeatedly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>법석거리다 [법썩꺼리다]</dt><br>
<dd>make a noise; fuss</dd><br>
<dd>소란스럽게 자꾸 떠들다.</dd><br>
<dd>To make a loud noise repeatedly.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>